{"tid":1391823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★【老店結業】又一Made In Hong Kong成絕唱 史蜜夫糖果廠結業","createTime":"2019-07-31T14:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T13:25:10.000Z","uid":19454,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c20c4af5fd554be73fb1a0d31ef3aca76fc19aaf","tid":1391823,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:23:35.000Z","msg":"史蜜夫糖果廠你未必記得，但一款印有藍色牛牛包裝的鳥結糖你大概會有印象。隨糖果廠第二代接班人方氏三兄弟退休，made in Hong Kong的牛奶鳥結糖、橙味軟糖、蜜瓜味軟糖等為港人熟悉的軟糖也將成絕唱，賣完市面現貨，近一甲子的品牌將正式劃上句號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/theculturist.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/%E5%8F%B2%E8%9C%9C%E5%A4%AB%E7%B3%96%E6%9E%9C%E5%BB%A0%E8%A3%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%9C%E7%93%9C%E5%91%B3%E8%BB%9F%E7%B3%96%E5%92%8C%E7%89%9B%E5%A5%B6%E9%B3%A5%E7%B5%90%E7%B3%96%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E5%9C%96%E7%89%87.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Ftheculturist.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F%25E5%258F%25B2%25E8%259C%259C%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E7%25B3%2596%25E6%259E%259C%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%259C%259C%25E7%2593%259C%25E5%2591%25B3%25E8%25BB%259F%25E7%25B3%2596%25E5%2592%258C%25E7%2589%259B%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E9%25B3%25A5%25E7%25B5%2590%25E7%25B3%2596%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%259C%2596%25E7%2589%2587.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C432%26ssl%3D1&h=34a4bec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一代史蜜夫糖果廠老闆方南，亦即方氏三兄弟（大哥方煒培、二哥方富泉和三弟方富成）的父親，於1960年和兩位朋友合資，購入一間位於旺角要清盤結業的「史密路士」糖果廠及機器，然後把名稱更改為「史蜜夫」展開經營，在1970年代方南購入觀塘廠房，續漸交由三兄弟打理經營至今。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n糖果廠高峰期工人多達30人，生產的糖果更遠銷中東地區及國內。在上世紀末，香港廠房北移潮也曾令大哥方煒培動心，欲將生產線轉至內地，<span style=\"color: red;\">但一想到made in Hong Kong變成made in China，感覺品牌好像會變得不再「馨香」，便打消了這念頭</span>。1997年起，不少大陸廠商紛紛加入製造糖果行業，made in Hong Kong當然不敵made in China的廉價攻勢，史蜜夫銷量大受影響。<br />\n<br />\n一直以不賺大錢，只要養活伙計和自己便足夠的精神經營，糖果廠隨年月員工降至大約6人，一星期也未必開機製一次糖。而方氏三兄弟最年輕的也是耳順之年，此時宣佈退休及結束糖果廠雖然可惜，但也算是一完美句號。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://theculturist.hk/2019/%e6%96%87%e5%8c%96%e5%82%b3%e6%89%bf/%e3%80%90%e8%80%81%e5%ba%97%e7%b5%90%e6%a5%ad%e3%80%91%e5%8f%88%e4%b8%80made-in-hong-kong%e6%88%90%e7%b5%95%e5%94%b1-%e5%8f%b2%e8%9c%9c%e5%a4%ab%e7%b3%96%e6%9e%9c%e5%bb%a0%e7%b5%90%e6%a5%ad/?fbclid=IwAR1DaC5AS2Ojh73vwcNdlISlxZkt_D-N7Hdfn1uZEb5BOUl55tpbe1r1A_w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheculturist.hk%2F2019%2F%25e6%2596%2587%25e5%258c%2596%25e5%2582%25b3%25e6%2589%25bf%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e8%2580%2581%25e5%25ba%2597%25e7%25b5%2590%25e6%25a5%25ad%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%258f%2588%25e4%25b8%2580made-in-hong-kong%25e6%2588%2590%25e7%25b5%2595%25e5%2594%25b1-%25e5%258f%25b2%25e8%259c%259c%25e5%25a4%25ab%25e7%25b3%2596%25e6%259e%259c%25e5%25bb%25a0%25e7%25b5%2590%25e6%25a5%25ad%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1DaC5AS2Ojh73vwcNdlISlxZkt_D-N7Hdfn1uZEb5BOUl55tpbe1r1A_w&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFolFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=d79a2246\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theculturist.hk/2019/%e6%96%87%e5%8c%96%e5%82%b3%e6%89%bf/%e3%80%90%e8%80%81%e5%ba%97%e7%b5%90%e6%a5%ad%e3%80%91%e5%8f%88%e4%b8%80made-in-hong-kong%e6%88%90%e7%b5%95%e5%94%b1-%e5%8f%b2%e8%9c%9c%e5%a4%ab%e7%b3%96%e6%9e%9c%e5%bb%a0%e7%b5%90%e6%a5%ad/?fbclid=IwAR1DaC5AS2Ojh73vwcNdlISlxZkt_D-N7Hdfn1uZEb5BOUl55tpbe1r1A_w</a>"},{"pid":"a12e215396b2ed581314b224dbca0806fadf870f","tid":1391823,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ddc792ed3fc5b317e4503e57f5748ef54327548","tid":1391823,"uid":243366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7cb8587d72f8734fcd83396dd304bef2de9f30","tid":1391823,"uid":4574,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:26:02.000Z","msg":"宣傳不足"},{"pid":"fc25438fe44bf2146d380e1a0162c37870e3d5d8","tid":1391823,"uid":276758,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:28:05.000Z