95%25e5%2594%25b1-%25e5%258f%25b2%25e8%259c%259c%25e5%25a4%25ab%25e7%25b3%2596%25e6%259e%259c%25e5%25bb%25a0%25e7%25b5%2590%25e6%25a5%25ad%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1DaC5AS2Ojh73vwcNdlISlxZkt_D-N7Hdfn1uZEb5BOUl55tpbe1r1A_w&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFolFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=d79a2246\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theculturist.hk/2019/%e6%96%87%e5%8c%96%e5%82%b3%e6%89%bf/%e3%80%90%e8%80%81%e5%ba%97%e7%b5%90%e6%a5%ad%e3%80%91%e5%8f%88%e4%b8%80made-in-hong-kong%e6%88%90%e7%b5%95%e5%94%b1-%e5%8f%b2%e8%9c%9c%e5%a4%ab%e7%b3%96%e6%9e%9c%e5%bb%a0%e7%b5%90%e6%a5%ad/?fbclid=IwAR1DaC5AS2Ojh73vwcNdlISlxZkt_D-N7Hdfn1uZEb5BOUl55tpbe1r1A_w</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16966cd405124b3139d92ec7eea97b57d5e2330f","tid":1391823,"uid":203813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:44:51.000Z","msg":"我好鍾意食<br />\n之前買都唔知係本土野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805e793a59b53d70443d0f07945b8638a67f7265","tid":1391823,"uid":84336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:30:10.000Z","msg":"記得睇電視同facebook都見過佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a969de36c7db6a89d83b851e28b7c78a6f8b5ed","tid":1391823,"uid":123112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:35:39.000Z","msg":"買過牛奶糖.. 但我覺得大白兔糖好食D, 加上而家已經唔鍾意食甜野, 食左幾粒成包都擺左係到無郁過"},{"pid":"75cce45533d640423dd63a76229784141918d31f","tid":1391823,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:37:19.000Z","msg":"太少售賣點"},{"pid":"7ce62f00e475e661a7107a0f69e38838b48890a9","tid":1391823,"uid":274537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:19:12.000Z","msg":"油尖旺或銅鑼灣哪裡能買到？"},{"pid":"3fff3c41ff74cecf5d3